attributionInfo.agentName: Jennie & Eddie Luxury Living Boston Team

description: Experience elevated city living in this stunning 12th-floor 1BR/1BA residence with 1 valet garage parking. The premier Southeast-facing home boasts floor-to-ceiling windows that frame breathtaking views of the Blue Hills. A built-in desk/workspace enhances the space, while the European Thermador kitchen suite with Wi-Fi-enabled appliances and Bosch washer & dryer provides the epitome of modern convenience. EchelonSeaport residents enjoy unparalleled luxury with 24/7 concierge service & doorman, and access to over 50,000 sq ft of amenities, including three pools, a hot tub, an indoor basketball court, a state-of-the-art fitness center, dedicated yoga and Pilates studios, a sports simulator, and a serene spa. Outdoor spaces feature lounge areas, fireplaces, grill stations, and the exclusive 22nd Floor Sky Lounge, offering panoramic views of the Seaport and beyond. Indulge in the ultimate urban lifestyle.
